# acme-petstore-api

Generated by ShipMCP from `Acme Petstore API`.

## What this project includes

- MCP stdio server
- Generated tool handlers from OpenAPI operations
- bearer auth preset
- Dockerfile
- GitHub Actions CI
- Smoke tests

## Generation filters

- include-paths=/pets* | exclude-operation-ids=create*
## Quick start

```bash
npm install
cp .env.example .env
npm run dev
```

## Generated tools

- `list_pets` -> GET /pets
- `get_pet` -> GET /pets/{petId}

## Notes

- Review generated tool names before publishing.
- Replace placeholder auth values in `.env`.
- Launch the server from a compatible stdio MCP client.
- Extend `src/client.ts` if your API needs custom signing or retries.
